$$ s^-_i = \theta \frac{\overline{U}_i - \overline{U}_{i-1}}{\Delta X},\quad 
 s^c_i = \frac{\overline{U}_{i+1} - \overline{U}_{i-1}}{2\Delta X},\quad
 s^+_i = \theta \frac{\overline{U}_{i+1} - \overline{U}_i}{\Delta X}$$
$$ s_i = \text{minmod}(s^-_i,s^c_i,s^+_i) = \begin{cases}
 \text{min}(s^-_i,s^c_i,s^+_i) & \text{if $s^-_i>0$\xc2\xa0$\land$ $s^c_i>0$ $\land$ $s^+_i>0$}\\
 \text{max}(s^-_i,s^c_i,s^+_i) & \text{if $s^-_i<0$ $\land$ $s^c_i<0$ $\land$ $s^+_i<0$}\\
 0 & \text{otherwise}
 \end{cases}$$
